            "c": "(3x + 3)",
            "d": "(2x + 1)"
          },
          "correct": "a",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "mp_birla",
          "explanation": "6x²+7x-3 = (3x-1)(2x+3). Divide by (3x-1) to get breadth = (2x+3). Verify: (3x-1)(2x+3)=6x²+9x-2x-3=6x²+7x-3 ✓."
        },
