          },
          "correct": "c",
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "The error is the missing middle term. (2a+3b)² = 4a²+2(2a)(3b)+9b² = 4a²+12ab+9b². Options c and d are identical — both are correct."
